title: Lineage Kamael Client
description:
This is SFX archive with latest Lineage II Client (Kamael).
The client is modified for run with http://www.kamael.ge x10 and x1500 servers but also you will find original system folder backed up as .bak so you can use it as an official one.

Further instruction how to run the client with www.kamael.ge servers you will find here: http://www.kamael.ge/detail.jsp 
and here: http://forum.kamael.ge/viewtopic.php?f=8&t=34
